===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*deyá¸±-}}
From {{inh|en|enm|dixionare}}, {{glossary|learned borrowing}} from {{der|en|ML.|dictiÅnÄrium}}, from {{der|en|la|dictiÅnÄrius}}, from {{m|la|dictiÅ||a speaking}}, from {{m|la|dictus}}, perfect past participle of {{m|la|dÄ«cÅ|t= to speak}} + {{m|la|-Ärium|t=room, place}}. {{surf|en|diction|-ary}}.

